}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/FeatureOfInterest",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Cosa cuya propiedad se está estimando o calculando en el curso de una Observación para llegar a un Resultado o cuya propiedad está siendo manipulada por un Actuador, o que está siendo muestreada o transformada en un acto de Muestreo."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Entidad de interés"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Feature Of Interest"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una cualidad observable (propiedad, característica) de una entidad de interés."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Propiedad observable"
  }, {
    "@value" : "Observable Property"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Acto de realizar un procedimiento (de observación) para estimar o calcular el valor de una propiedad de una característica de interés. Se vincula a un sensor para describir qué realizó la observación y cómo; se vincula a una propiedad observable para describir de qué propiedad es la estimación del resultado, y a una característica de interés para detallar con qué se asoció esa propiedad."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Observación"
  }, {
    "@value" : "Observation"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sensor",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Sistema que implementa un procedimiento de observación para determinar el valor de una Propiedad observable.Puede ser un dispositivo, una infraestructura, un agente (incluyendo humanos) o software (simulación). Un sensor responde a un estímulo, por ejemplo, un cambio en el entorno o datos de entrada compuestos por los resultados de observaciones previas."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Sensor"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Sensor"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/hasFeatureOfInterest",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una relación entre una Observación y la entidad cuya calidad fue observada, o entre una Actuación y la entidad cuya propiedad fue modificada, o entre un acto de muestreo y la entidad que fue muestreada."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "tiene entidad de interés"
  }, {
    "@value" : "has feature of interest"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/FeatureOfInterest"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/hasSimpleResult",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty" ],
  "http://schema.org/domainIncludes" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Actuation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservationCollection"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sampling"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The simple value of an Observation or Actuation or act of Sampling."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/common/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "has simple result"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The simple value of an Observation or Actuation or act of Sampling."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "For instance, the values 23 or true."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/madeBySensor",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Relación entre una observación y el sensor que realiza la observación."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "made by sensor or observer"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "realizado por sensor u observador"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sensor"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/observedProperty",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://schema.org/domainIncludes" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservationCollection"
  } ],
  "http://schema.org/rangeIncludes" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Property"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Relation linking an Observation to the property that was observed. The ObservableProperty should be a property of the FeatureOfInterest (linked by hasFeatureOfInterest) of this Observation."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/obs/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "observed property"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/wasObservedBy"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "\n  relation from an Observation or ObservationCollection to the property that was observed\n  "
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Relation linking an Observation to the property that was observed. The ObservableProperty should be a property of the FeatureOfInterest (linked by hasFeatureOfInterest) of this Observation."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "\n  'observed property' covers the concepts referred to in [VIM] as 'measurand' (quantitative values) and 'examinand' (categorical and nominal values — [VIM4]), as well as complex and structured properties whose values may be represented as lists, vectors, arrays, rasters, geometries, etc. More specific terms are used in other contexts for related concepts, such as 'analyte' (chemistry) and 'determinand' (water quality).\n  "
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/observes",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Relación entre un sensor y una propiedad observable que es capaz de detectar."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sensor"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "observa"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "observes"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/phenomenonTime",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty" ],
  "http://schema.org/domainIncludes" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Actuation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservationCollection"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sampling"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "El momento en que el resultado de una observación, actuación o muestreo se aplica a la entidad de interés. No necesariamente coincide con el momento del resultado. Puede ser un intervalo, un instante o alguna otra entidad temporal compuesta."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The time that the Result of an Observation, Actuation or Sampling applies to the FeatureOfInterest. Not necessarily the same as the resultTime. May be an Interval or an Instant, or some other compound TemporalEntity."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/common/"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "momento del fenómeno"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "phenomenon time"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The time that the Result of an Observation, Actuation or Sampling applies to the FeatureOfInterest. Not necessarily the same as the resultTime. May be an Interval or an Instant, or some other compound TemporalEntity."
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/resultTime",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty" ],
  "http://schema.org/domainIncludes" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Actuation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservationCollection"
  }, {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Sampling"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The result time is the instant of time when the Observation, Actuation or Sampling activity was completed."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/Observation"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy" : [ {
